27:32.686 --> 27:34.788
That is affected me now.

27:34.828 --> 27:35.389
Oh, thanks, Carol.

27:37.471 --> 27:38.712
And thinking about...

27:39.130 --> 27:44.175
What are the possibilities or what the effects of libraries?

27:44.195 --> 27:47.418
I guess all of us had experiences of our own.

27:48.559 --> 28:09.120
