44:43.834 --> 44:44.095
Really?

44:44.115 --> 44:45.276
A young guy?

44:45.336 --> 44:45.597
Yeah.

44:45.657 --> 44:48.321
And so this stuff... He's got lots more.

44:48.381 --> 44:51.866
So one hopes you'll get more.

44:52.367 --> 44:54.490
Yeah, that's right.

44:54.510 --> 45:04.185
